										<li id="comment-103466" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='Dread Knight`s avatar' src='http://AncientBeast.com/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">11</div>
